/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a moment on a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape below. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Trees are interspersed between the buildings, adding a touch of nature to the urban setting. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many cities. The sun shines brightly in the top right corner of the image, casting light and shadows that add depth to the scene.
